# plaintasks_howto.todo

Heading:      # heading/project title colon
☐ Anything with colon at the end of the line is a project title, you can also nest projects by indenting them.

☐ ⌘ Enter     # create new task
☐ ⌘ d         # Done task
☐ ⌘ SHIFT a     #archive done task
✘ CTRL c - cancel task @cancelled (17-06-15 17:26)
☐ You can add tags using @ sign; right click | Filter by Tag
    ☐ to unfold all press ⌘+k, ⌘+j

-- tab        # create separator
